Hi,

Please follow the below steps,

&nbsp; &nbsp; 1. Click on "Settings" icon from "Site Manager".

&nbsp; &nbsp; 2. Adjust time "Adjust Time" field as per your location timing. You can also click on "view current date/time" in front of same field to compare with server time.

&nbsp; &nbsp; 3. Set "Show Article Date = Posting Date"

&nbsp; &nbsp; 4. Click on "submit".

Resubmit one article for changes to take effect.

Please visit your homepage and press Ctrl+F5 or click on reload icon on your browser to see the updated changes.

Thank you.
